OL,3,CTemporary exemption certificates
OL,4,Cconsidered to tackle MOT waiting lists
OL,6,FMeasures to try and tackle MOT waiting
OL,7,Flists in Northern Ireland have been
OL,8,Foutlined by the infrastructure
OL,9,Fminister.
OL,11,FJohn O'Dowd says he will explore the
OL,12,Fintroduction of temporary exemption
OL,13,Fcertificates and proposals to consult
OL,14,Fon testing every two years.
OL,16,FHe added that the DVA has 55 vacancies
OL,17,Ffor examiners across its test centres
OL,18,Fand said he hopes the successful
OL,19,Fcandidates can be in place from early
OL,20,FJune.
