OL,6,F"I have asked the DVA to release
OL,7,Fadditional appointments for these new
OL,8,Frecruits as soon as possible," the
OL,9,Fminister told the Assembly during a
OL,10,Fdebate on Monday evening.
OL,12,F"55 new examiners will provide the
OL,13,Fcapacity for a hugely significant
OL,14,Fincrease in appointments in a year and
OL,15,Fwill be expected to have a positive
OL,16,Fimpact for our customers."
