OL,6,FMr O'Dowd continued: "In addition,
OL,7,Fanyone who cannot secure an
OL,8,Fappointment before their tax expires,
OL,9,For their tax has already expired, have
OL,10,Fbeen advised to contact the DVA
OL,11,Fcustomer services team for an urgent
OL,12,FMOT appointment.
OL,14,F"The DVA currently asks customers to
OL,15,Fcontact them within five days of their
OL,16,Ftax expiry date, but I can confirm
OL,17,Fthat, with immediate effect, the DVA
OL,18,Fis extending this window to ten days
OL,19,Fto provide more flexibility for
OL,20,Fcustomers and reduce any anxiety."
