OL,4,Cconsidered to tackle MOT waiting lists
OL,6,FDUP MLA Deborah Erskine proposed a
OL,7,Fmotion to the Assembly to "stress the
OL,8,Fimportance of fair and timely access
OL,9,Fto vehicle testing across Northern
OL,10,FIreland", and "believes it is
OL,11,Funacceptable that many motorists are
OL,12,Ffacing lengthy delays to secure an MOT
OL,13,Fappointment".
OL,15,FThe motion also called on the minister
OL,16,Fto "bring forward an ambitious and
OL,17,Fcosted plan to tackle the backlog in
OL,18,Ftests, cut waiting times, deal with
OL,19,F'no shows' and ensure fairer access
OL,20,Ffor those who are currently
OL,21,Fdisadvantaged as soon as possible".
