OL,6,FThe motion was passed as well as an
OL,7,FSDLP amendment calling for a
OL,8,Fconsultation on biennial testing.
OL,10,FSpeaking in the chamber, Ms Erskine
OL,11,Fsaid the motion was of importance to
OL,12,F"thousands of people in Northern
OL,13,FIreland at this time".
OL,15,FShe said the current system is no
OL,16,Flonger fit for purpose and is due for
OL,17,Fan overhaul.
