OL,6,FShe quoted Chief Executive of the
OL,7,FDriver and Vehicle Agency (DVA),
OL,8,FJeremy Logan who recently said a 72-
OL,9,Fday wait for a test is the new normal,
OL,10,Fadding "it shouldn't be and we
OL,11,Fshouldn't accept that".
OL,13,FMs Erskine said she appreciated the
OL,14,Fwork of those who carry out the tests,
OL,15,Fbut said there must be measures to
OL,16,Faddress the issues.
