OL,6,FResponding, Mr O'Dowd said he
OL,7,Frecognised the frustration felt by
OL,8,Fmotorists waiting for a test and said
OL,9,Fhe agreed that they should have fair
OL,10,Fand timely access to vehicle testing.
OL,12,FHe said in 2022/2023, the DVA
OL,13,Fconducted more than 1.5 million
OL,14,Fvehicle tests, the highest number ever
OL,15,Frecorded in a year, by offering
OL,16,Fappointments around the week and on
OL,17,Fbank holidays.
